# Task ID-XX: Brief description of what was done
#
# Longer description explaining:
# - What specific changes were made
# - Why these changes were necessary 
# - Any important implementation details
#
# Examples:
# Task 55: Ensure validation stages appear in settings-defined order in analytics page
# Task 66: Implement automated todo completion via pre-commit hooks
#
# Guidelines:
# - Start with "Task ID-XX:" where XX is the task number from todo-list.json
# - Use present tense ("Add feature" not "Added feature")
# - Keep the first line under 72 characters
# - Reference issue numbers if applicable
# - Explain the "why" not just the "what"
#
# This commit format enables automatic todo list updates when commits succeed.